"Main_Content":
"Kevin Durant has spent months quietly roasting a Warriors rookie's Instagram
page
By: Andrew Joseph | November 7
"Time":
2017 1:33 pm
KD在勇士菜鳥Boucher的IG上已經持續了幾個月的攻擊

Kevin Durant’s secret Instagram account was one of the offseason’s more
entertaining NBA sagas
"Max_Word_Indicator":
but it turns out that Durant’s official Instagram
account has also been busy the past couple months … at the expense of a
Warriors rookie.
KD的匿名帳號在季後帶了一些娛樂
column6:
然而他的官方帳號最近幾個月也沒閒著...攻擊一名勇
士菜鳥

This week
column7:
NBA fans noticed that Durant has been roasting the Instagram posts
of undrafted Warriors rookie Chris Boucher since September.
NBA的粉絲發現KD從九月開始在Chris Boucher的IG上鬧了已經好一陣子

Durant really hasn’t held back.
KD沒有要停止的意思

https://i.imgur.com/Z8ASvLu.png
KD: U trash lol (你這個垃圾 呵呵)

This has continued for quite some time.
這已經持續了好一陣子

https://i.imgur.com/eiutxU4.png
KD: L L L

All of the L’s — and to his credit
column8:
Boucher has been a good sport about
Durant’s social-media trolling.

https://i.imgur.com/xu2cmFr.png
Durant also hasn’t let Boucher’s assignment to G-League affiliate Santa
Cruz prevent the tormenting. When Durant noticed that Boucher wore Nike KD
sneakers in his Oregon photo
column9:
the Warriors star jumped right back in Boucher’
s comment section.
KD沒有在該菜鳥下放發展練盟後停止.在KD發現Boucher大學穿過KD的鞋後他又開始了

https://i.imgur.com/N3fjink.jpg
KD:Take my shoes off chump (蠢貨 把我的鞋子脫掉)

Durant eventually started to feel bad about his comments. After calling
Boucher ugly
column10:
Durant wanted to let the rookie know that it was all in good
fun.
最終KD覺得這樣不太好.在稱他醜之後
column11:
KD希望菜鳥知道這只是在玩

See
column12:
that was nice of him.

https://i.imgur.com/V4Erf3f.png
KD:U ugly as s*** (你醜的跟***一樣)
KD:u still my rook
column13:
u know I got love for ya lol (你知道我是愛你的 呵呵)

http://tinyurl.com/y7p4wbdb



https://i.imgur.com/R8NM5Fo.png
#1PQAlPyy (NBA)落選Boucher與勇士簽約：我曾告訴媽媽我們不會餓肚子了
